input_str: In late January, the Air Force banned TogetherWeServed.com, a military-themed social networking site, for being a security "nightmare." Now, Air Force officials are admitting "to unfairly singling out" the site, which "does not pose any extra risk than most chat rooms or other online communities," *Stars & Stripes' *Leo Shane reports. "Site owners said the retraction may have come too late to help their online business."
